FBIS4-25704 "drchi114_o_94002" FBIS-CHI-94-114 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 REGIONAL AFFAIRS East Region Shandong Deals Blows to Maritime Offenders Shandong Deals Blows to Maritime Offenders SK1406031894 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in Mandarin 2300 GMT 13 June 94 SK1406031894 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network Mandarin BFN [Text] SHANDONG QINGNIAN BAO, published on 13 June, carries an article that discloses that since the beginning of this year, the province's armed border defense police forces have dealt strict blows to coastal and maritime offenders. They have captured 151 criminals and cracked down on 169 cases of various categories, obviously improving the public security and social order of coastal areas.
